\quad \sum_{s \in S} ( \frac{1}{s} ) \\ > \; \sum_{s \in S \setminus \{c\}} ( \frac{1}{s} ) \\ = \; \sum_{k=1}^{\infty} ( \frac{1}{c + 2kp} ) \\ > \; \sum_{k=1}^{\infty} ( \frac{1}{2(k+1)p} ) \\ = \; \frac{1}{2p} \sum_{k=0}^{\infty} \frac{1}{k} \\ = +\infty
